<law type="statute"><section><amendatorysection amended="yes" chaptername="State Institutions" statutenumber="83-371"><bookinfo>Revised Statutes Cumulative Supplement, 2026</bookinfo><statuteno>83-371</statuteno><catchline>Department; rules and regulations.</catchline><para>Pursuant to the provisions of the Administrative Procedure Act, the department shall adopt and promulgate appropriate rules and regulations for making the determinations required by sections 83-227.01, 83-227.02, 83-350, and 83-363 to 83-379.</para></amendatorysection></section><source><para>Laws 1969, c. 812, &#167; 9, p. 3053; </para><para>Laws 2026, LB1048, &#167; 36. </para><effectivedate>July 18, 2026</effectivedate></source><crossreference><para><emphasis>Administrative Procedure Act,</emphasis> see section 84-920.</para></crossreference></law>
